Thus we can have a button that calls setIsModalOpen(true) and setSelectedMovie(movie). Then the Dialog component will open.

Thus we don't need DialogTrigger. We can just use DialogContent with open prop.

But Shadcn's Dialog component includes DialogTrigger and DialogContent. The Dialog component is a wrapper that includes the portal. The DialogTrigger is optional. If we don't use DialogTrigger, we can still control open via prop.

